  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LUCAS JAMES ANDERSON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The contingent beneficiary, son of the insured. Receives 50% of the death benefit if the primary beneficiary predeceases the insured."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fde85eeed0e7ef938be9b3d18c3183ef</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DOCUMENTATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"All required documentation must be received for a claim to be processed."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;20 YEARS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DURATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The term of the policy, which will expire on January 15, 2044."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fde85eeed0e7ef938be9b3d18c3183ef</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;P.O. BOX 5000&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ADDRESS"</data>
  <data key="d4">"P.O. Box 5000 is the mailing address for claims submissions."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;JANUARY 15, 2024&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DATE"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The date on which the life insurance policy was issued."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy was issued on January 15, 2024."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fde85eeed0e7ef938be9b3d18c3183ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CONVERSION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Conversion must occur before the earlier of the policy expiry date or the insured's 65th birthday."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;EVIDENCE OF INSURABILITY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Evidence of insurability refers to medical exams or health information required to prove eligibility for insurance."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CLASS OF PERMANENT POLICY SELECTED&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The type or level of permanent policy chosen during conversion, such as whole life or universal life."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;INSURED&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The insured is the individual whose life is covered by the policy."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;COVERAGE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Coverage continues during the grace period, which is a specified time after the due date when the policy remains active despite late payment."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SECTION 2: COVERAGE DETAILS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"SECTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The section detailing the death benefit, policy term, premium amount, and payment mode."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fde85eeed0e7ef938be9b3d18c3183ef</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ALTERNATE SETTLEMENT OPTION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"SETTLEMENT_OPTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A payment method chosen by the beneficiary instead of a lump sum, such as installments or annuity."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fde85eeed0e7ef938be9b3d18c3183ef</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;WRITTEN NOTICE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Written notice must be received at the home office for an assignment to be binding."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DEATH BENEFIT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The amount of money payable to the beneficiary upon the death of the insured during the policy term, as defined in Section 4.1."&lt;SEP&gt;"The death benefit is adjusted based on the correct age and sex."&lt;SEP&gt;"The death benefit is the amount paid to the beneficiary upon the insured's death."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fde85eeed0e7ef938be9b3d18c3183ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;INCONTESTABILITY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Incontestability is a clause that prevents the insurer from challenging the policy's validity after it has been in force for two years."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;JANUARY 15, 2044&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DATE"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The expiration date of the policy term."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fde85eeed0e7ef938be9b3d18c3183ef</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HARTFORD&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"LOCATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Hartford is the city where the claims department is located."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;20-YEAR LEVEL TERM LIFE INSURANCE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"POLICY_TYPE"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A type of life insurance that provides coverage for a fixed 20-year term with a level death benefit and fixed premiums."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fde85eeed0e7ef938be9b3d18c3183ef</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BENEFICIARY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The beneficiary is the individual designated to receive the death benefit."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;POLICY EXPIRY DATE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DATE"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The policy expiry date is the date when the policy ends unless renewed or converted."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ISSUE DATE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DATE"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The issue date is the date when the policy is issued."&lt;SEP&gt;"The issue date is the starting point for the incontestability period."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PREMIUM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The premium for the new policy is determined based on the insured's attained age, amount of coverage, and policy class."&lt;SEP&gt;"The premium is the amount paid by the policyholder to maintain the insurance policy."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SECTION 3: BENEFICIARY DESIGNATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"SECTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The section specifying the primary and contingent beneficiaries and their respective shares."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fde85eeed0e7ef938be9b3d18c3183ef</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;POLICY LAPSE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The termination of coverage when a premium is not paid within the grace period."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fde85eeed0e7ef938be9b3d18c3183ef</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HOME OFFICE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"LOCATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The home office is the central administrative office of the insurer."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bd95d6b8fc6079aaa04ca42829989a10</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PREMIUM DUE DATE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The 15th day of each month, when the monthly premium is due for payment."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fde85eeed0e7ef938be9b3d18c3183ef</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TWO YEARS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"TIME PERIOD"</data>
